text: Zoom, Amazon, LinkedIn, Alibaba dan eBay terancam tidak bisa di akses lagi di Indonesia, karena pihak pengelola platform tersebut, belum mendaftarkan PSE lingkup privat mereka ke kementerian Kominfo RI.semua produk layanan meta Indonesia dan Google Indonesia sudah terdaftar.
en_text: Zoom, Amazon, LinkedIn, Alibaba and Ebay are threatened with no more accessed in Indonesia, because the platform manager has not registered their private scope to the Ministry of Communication and Information.
